CREATE TABLE [dbo].[customers]
( 
	[id] [varchar](256)  NULL,
	[name] [varchar](256)  NULL,
	[lastname] [varchar](256)  NULL,
	[age] [SMALLINT]  NULL,
	[country] [varchar](256)  NULL,
	[city] [varchar](256)  NULL,
	[postcode] [varchar](256)  NULL,
	[street] [varchar](256)  NULL,
	[building] [varchar](256)  NULL
)
